										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>It&#8217;s finally October, and Sherlock Day&#8230;  I mean, &#8220;Halloween&#8221; is swiftly approaching.  So, here&#8217;s a load of silly old &#8216;ghost&#8217; photos to kick off my favorite month in the year.  Enjoy the mirth and cleverness of the early photoshoppers!</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-726 aligncenter" alt="3a9060cba02e25bb3073ea6b0150d410" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/3a9060cba02e25bb3073ea6b0150d410.jpg" width="500" height="635" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/3a9060cba02e25bb3073ea6b0150d410.jpg 500w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/3a9060cba02e25bb3073ea6b0150d410-236x300.jpg 236w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" />  <a href="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/530c6cfa46dc6a698ccfe2454afa2001.jpg" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone  wp-image-727" alt="530c6cfa46dc6a698ccfe2454afa2001" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/530c6cfa46dc6a698ccfe2454afa2001.jpg" width="280" height="374" /></a> <a href="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/a-ghost-of-the-victorian-age-halloween-16517212-300-416.jpg" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone  wp-image-731" alt="A-ghost-of-the-victorian-age-halloween-16517212-300-416" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/a-ghost-of-the-victorian-age-halloween-16517212-300-416.jpg" width="270" height="374" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/a-ghost-of-the-victorian-age-halloween-16517212-300-416.jpg 300w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/a-ghost-of-the-victorian-age-halloween-16517212-300-416-216x300.jpg 216w" sizes="(max-width: 270px) 100vw, 270px" /></a></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-730 aligncenter" alt="03073788fde2a1043b4121f00d2ae0ab" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/03073788fde2a1043b4121f00d2ae0ab.jpg" width="587" height="378" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/03073788fde2a1043b4121f00d2ae0ab.jpg 652w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/03073788fde2a1043b4121f00d2ae0ab-300x193.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 587px) 100vw, 587px" /><a href="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/1.jpg" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone  wp-image-751" alt="1" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/1.jpg" width="275" height="288" /></a> <a href="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2.jpg" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone  wp-image-752" alt="2" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2.jpg" width="275" height="288" /></a> <img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-754 aligncenter" alt="4" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/4.jpg" width="604" height="533" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/4.jpg 604w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/4-300x264.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 604px) 100vw, 604px" /><a href="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/3.jpg" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone  wp-image-753" alt="3" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/3.jpg" width="275" height="320" /></a>  <a href="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/5.jpg" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone  wp-image-755" alt="5" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/5.jpg" width="275" height="320" /></a> <img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-756 aligncenter" alt="6" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/6.jpg" width="397" height="533" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/6.jpg 397w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/6-223x300.jpg 223w" sizes="(max-width: 397px) 100vw, 397px" /></p>
