										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Happy August, internet!  Today&#8217;s image dump of awesome comes from <a href="http://insectlabstudio.com/" target="_blank">Insect Lab Studio</a>, one of the coolest/creepiest sites I&#8217;ve found.  These wonderful little sculptures are for sale on the site, so by the time this post is up some of these might already be sold.  Get &#8216;um while they&#8217;re hot!  Enjoy!</p>
